@startuml
title Alarm Clock Control

[*] --> Off

state Off
state AlarmActivated
state AlarmRinging
state AlarmStopped
state Idle

Off : entry / Display Welcome

Off --> AlarmActivated : Set Alarm Time / Activate Alarm

AlarmActivated --> AlarmRinging : Current Time Matches Alarm Time / Start Alarm

AlarmRinging --> AlarmStopped : Stop Alarm / Stop Alarm

AlarmActivated --> AlarmStopped : Turn Off Alarm / Turn Off Alarm

AlarmStopped --> AlarmActivated : Next Scheduled Alarm Time / Activate Next Alarm

AlarmRinging --> Idle : Alarm Stopped / Display Idle

AlarmStopped --> Idle : Alarm Stopped / Display Idle

Idle --> Off : Power Off / Display Off

@enduml
